{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-20T04:42:23.655Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"large language model (LLM)"},{"type":"text","text":" made by Anthropic. At its core, it’s a machine that does one simple thing astonishingly well:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Given a sequence of words (or tokens), predict the most likely next word."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"That’s it. No hidden “brain” or consciousness. Everything Claude does—answering questions, writing essays, coding, reasoning—comes from this single ability, scaled up to billions of parameters and trained on huge amounts of text."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Imagine you’re filling in missing words in a sentence:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“The cat sat on the _”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Your brain guesses something like "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“mat”"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“floor”"},{"type":"text","text":" because that’s what usually comes next. Claude does the same thing, but with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"tokens"},{"type":"text","text":" (small chunks of text) and with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"math"},{"type":"text","text":", not feelings."}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It sees: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"[\"The\", \"cat\", \"sat\", \"on\", \"the\"]"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It calculates: “What’s the most likely next token?”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It picks: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"[\"mat\"]"},{"type":"text","text":" (or something similar)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Then it repeats: sees "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"[\"The\", \"cat\", \"sat\", \"on\", \"the\", \"mat\"]"},{"type":"text","text":" and predicts the next token again."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"By doing this "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"one token at a time"},{"type":"text","text":", over and over, it generates full sentences, paragraphs, and even entire programs."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 1: Turn text into tokens"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude doesn’t read raw words. It first breaks your input into "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"tokens"},{"type":"text","text":", which are like “mini-words”:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Common words: “the” → one token"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Longer/rare words: “understanding” → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"[\"under\", \"standing\"]"},{"type":"text","text":" (two tokens)"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This lets Claude handle any word, even ones it’s never seen before."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 2: Turn tokens into numbers (vectors)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each token is converted into a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"list of numbers"},{"type":"text","text":" (a vector) called an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"embedding"},{"type":"text","text":". This is like giving each token a “position” in a huge mathematical space where similar words are close together."}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“cat” and “dog” → vectors near each other"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“cat” and “car” → vectors farther apart"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"These vectors are learned during training."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 3: Let tokens “look at” each other (self-attention)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude uses a special neural network called a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Transformer"},{"type":"text","text":". The key idea is "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"self-attention"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each token can “look at” all the other tokens in the sentence."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It asks: “Which other tokens are most important for understanding me?”"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“The animal didn’t cross the street because it was tired.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude learns that "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“it”"},{"type":"text","text":" refers to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“animal”"},{"type":"text","text":", not “street,” by paying more attention to “animal” when processing “it”."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is done with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Query, Key, and Value"},{"type":"text","text":" vectors:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Query"},{"type":"text","text":": “What am I looking for?”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key"},{"type":"text","text":": “What am I offering?”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Value"},{"type":"text","text":": “What information do I actually carry?”"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tokens compare Queries and Keys to decide how much to pay attention to each other’s Values."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 4: Stack many layers of processing"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude’s model has many "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"layers"},{"type":"text","text":" of these attention + feed-forward blocks:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Layer 1: learns simple patterns (e.g., word relationships)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Layer 2: learns more complex patterns (e.g., phrases)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"..."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Layer N: learns very abstract patterns (e.g., reasoning, style)"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each layer refines the representation a bit more. By the end, the model has a deep, context-aware understanding of the entire input."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 5: Predict the next token"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"At the top layer, Claude produces a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"probability distribution"},{"type":"text","text":" over all possible next tokens:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“mat”: 80%"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“floor”: 10%"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“table”: 5%"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"..."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It then "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"chooses"},{"type":"text","text":" one token:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Often the most likely (greedy), or"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sometimes a random one based on probabilities (sampling), controlled by "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"temperature"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Low temperature = more focused, predictable"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High temperature = more creative, random"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 6: Repeat until the answer is done"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"After picking the next token:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Add it to the input"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Run the model again"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Predict the next token"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Repeat until:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It decides to stop (e.g., sees a stop token)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Or it hits a max length"}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is called "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"autoregressive generation"},{"type":"text","text":": one token at a time, each conditioned on everything before it."}]}]}}
